{"title":"Kilian Bron follows a fire-lit drone through Cappadocia in Follow the Light","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/16/kilian-bron-follows-a-fire-lit-drone-through-cappadocia-in-follow-the-light/","date":1613491248000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>Shortly after treating us to Kilian Bron riding with Red Bull’s flying squirrels in <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/12/07/must-watch-kilian-brons-outdoor-synchrony-captures-wheeled-winged-action-in-art-form/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Outdoor Synchrony</a>, Commencal are spoiling us with yet another artfully shot shreddit. This time, the jaw-dropping backdrop is Cappadocia, Turkey. Kilian spent two weeks in this mesmerizing location, scoping out insane lines aboard is META AM.</p><p>We got a <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/01/18/must-watch-kilian-bron-flies-through-hot-air-balloons-in-turkey-for-gopro-award/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">preview of this project</a> earlier in the year as Bron realized that the footage would be a great entry into the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/12/19/gopros-hero9-black-million-dollar-highlight-video-doesnt-disappoint/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GoPro HERO9 Black Million Dollar video challenge</a>. Of course, with incredible riding and an unmatched background, the clip earned Kilian Bron and Pierre Dupont $17,000 a piece in the contest. But the real reason they were in Cappadocia was for this feature project for Commencal bikes, which was definitely worth the wait…</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/kilian-bron-follow-the-light-cappadocia-turkey.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/kilian-bron-follow-the-light-cappadocia-turkey.jpg\" alt=\"kilian bron cappadocia turkey follow the light fire lit drone\" width=\"1200\"